videos.description: LJ Figueroa picks off Jamorko Pickett's pass then takes it the other way to the rim for a strong two-handed finish.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Figueroa steals and slams for St. John's) 2019/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Figueroa steals and slams for St. John's

videos.description: Mac McClung brings it up the floor and rips a no-look pass down low to Josh LeBlanc, who hammers down a two-handed jam to extend Georgetown's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McClung makes no-look pass to LeBlanc for dunk) 2019/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: McClung makes no-look pass to LeBlanc for dunk

videos.description: Mac McClung drives the lane and somehow emerges out of traffic to bank in a midrange jumper, giving the Hoyas a 50-48 lead over the Red Storm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McClung goes through 3 defenders to hit fadeaway bank shot) 2019/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: McClung goes through 3 defenders to hit fadeaway bank shot

videos.description: Mac McClung shows off his range with a deep 3-ball, then follows it up with another one on the next possession to make it 73-64 Hoyas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McClung hits back-to-back triples from NBA range) 2019/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: McClung hits back-to-back triples from NBA range

videos.description: LJ Figueroa misses the go-ahead 3-pointer for St. John's and after several missed putback attempts, Mac McClung breaks free for a two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McClung swings momentum with huge dunk late in game) 2019/01/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: McClung swings momentum with huge dunk late in game
